          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium heat</p><p>Slice your <strong>brioche bun[s]</strong> in half</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> brioche halves</strong> to the pan, cut-side down, and cook for 3-4 min or until golden</p><p>Once golden, transfer to a plate and set aside for later</p>",
